TITLE: Configuring Orval with JavaScript configuration file
DESCRIPTION: Example of an Orval configuration file that defines input and output paths for generating API client code from an OpenAPI specification file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/docs/src/pages/quick-start.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = {
  'petstore-file': {
    input: './petstore.yaml',
    output: './src/petstore.ts',
  },
};
```

