TITLE: Using Generated Zod Schemas for Validation and Type Inference
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to use the generated Zod schemas for both data validation with parse() and for TypeScript type inference with z.infer.
SOURCE: https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/docs/src/pages/guides/zod.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
