TITLE: FormData Serialization: 'explode' Strategy
DESCRIPTION: Generated TypeScript code for FormData creation using the 'explode' strategy, which flattens nested objects and arrays into individual form fields with indexed notation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/docs/src/pages/reference/configuration/output.md#2025-04-22_snippet_48

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const formData = new FormData();
if (pet.name !== undefined) {
  formData.append(`name`, pet.name);
}
if (pet.age !== undefined) {
  formData.append(`age`, pet.age.toString());
}
if (pet.relatives !== undefined) {
  pet.relatives.forEach((value, index) => {
    if (value.name !== undefined) {
      formData.append(`relatives[${index}].name`, value.name);
    }
    if (value.colors !== undefined) {
      value.colors.forEach((value, index1) =>
        formData.append(`relatives[${index}].colors[${index1}]`, value),
      );
    }
  });
}
```

