SOURCE: https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/samples/react-query/basic/public/robots.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
# https://www.robotstxt.org/robotstxt.html
User-agent: *
Disallow:
```

