TITLE: Configuring MCP Server in AI Agent
DESCRIPTION: JSON configuration for setting up the MCP Petstore server in the 'cline' AI agent. The configuration specifies the Docker command and arguments needed to run the server container.
SOURCE: https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/samples/mcp/petstore/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "petstore": {
      "command": "docker",
      "args": [
        "run",
        "-i",
        "--rm",
        "mcp-petstore"
      ],
      "disabled": false,
      "alwaysAllow": []
    },
  }
}
```

