TITLE: Configuring Full Website Access in robots.txt
DESCRIPTION: This configuration allows all web crawlers and bots unrestricted access to the entire website. The universal wildcard user-agent (*) targets all bots, while the empty Disallow directive indicates no paths are restricted.
SOURCE: https://github.com/orval-labs/orval/blob/master/docs/public/robots.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: robots.txt
CODE:
```
User-agent: *
Disallow:
```

